title: Motorcycle Parking - Unmetered
description:
A. SUMMARY 
Locations and space count of unmetered motorcycle parking for the City of San Francisco.

B. METHODOLOGY  
Manually updated when MTA Board resolutions are passed 

C. UPDATE FREQUENCY  
Updated infrequently, several times a year at most 

D. OTHER CRITICAL INFO  
Includes UNMETERED motorcycles spaces only. Metered motorcycle spaces can be found in the Meters dataset (where cap color = black).
